{"id":155940,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2011/05/google宣布手机电子钱包，paypal起诉google/","date":"2011-05-28T05:30:47Z","modified":"2011-05-28T05:30:47Z","title":"Google宣布手机电子钱包，PayPal起诉Google","content":"<p>Google宣布了Google Wallet，基于近场通讯技术（NFC）的手机支付系统。Android手机用户在付费时只需让收银台阅读器感应一下手机即可。 移动支付蕴藏的商机，不仅吸引了银行、信用卡公司等传统企业的目光，也吸引了无线运营商、手机制造商等业的关注。移动支付的吸引力在于它能为消费者提供省时的支付方法。而通过移动支付平台向潜在客户群发送优惠券和广告信息则蕴含着更大的商机。Google Wallet和Google Offers将于今年夏天正式推出。未来Google可能会通过Google Offers服务发送优惠券，用户的代价将是失去隐私权。 彭博社报导，PayPal起诉Google，指控其盗用PayPal的移动支付业务商业机密。<img border=\"0\" height=\"1\" src=\"http://solidot.org.feedsportal.com/c/33236/f/556826/s/154c7e7f/mf.gif\" width=\"1\" /></p>\n<div>\n<table border=\"0\">\n<tr>\n<td valign=\"middle\"><a href=\"http://res.feedsportal.com/viral/sendemail2.html?title=Google%E5%AE%A3%E5%B8%83%E6%89%8B%E6%9C%BA%E7%94%B5%E5%AD%90%E9%92%B1%E5%8C%85%EF%BC%8CPayPal%E8%B5%B7%E8%AF%89Google&#038;link=http%3A%2F%2Fit.solidot.org%2Farticle.pl%3Fsid%3D11%2F05%2F27%2F0614214%26amp%3Bfrom%3Drss\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/images/emailthis2.gif\" /></a></td>\n<td valign=\"middle\"><a href=\"http://res.feedsportal.com/viral/bookmark.cfm?title=Google%E5%AE%A3%E5%B8%83%E6%89%8B%E6%9C%BA%E7%94%B5%E5%AD%90%E9%92%B1%E5%8C%85%EF%BC%8CPayPal%E8%B5%B7%E8%AF%89Google&#038;link=http%3A%2F%2Fit.solidot.org%2Farticle.pl%3Fsid%3D11%2F05%2F27%2F0614214%26amp%3Bfrom%3Drss\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/images/bookmark.gif\" /></a></td>\n</tr>\n</table>\n</div>\n<p><a href=\"http://da.feedsportal.com/r/101094717259/u/49/f/556826/c/33236/s/154c7e7f/a2.htm\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://da.feedsportal.com/r/101094717259/u/49/f/556826/c/33236/s/154c7e7f/a2.img\" /></a></p>\n<div>\n<a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/solidot?a=4JXRul9AIew:jHRhU2WCn7c:yIl2AUoC8zA\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/solidot?d=yIl2AUoC8zA\" /></a> <a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/solidot?a=4JXRul9AIew:jHRhU2WCn7c:7Q72WNTA